Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:26.35,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,160)}壞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:26.77,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,195)}孩子
